{"id":326995,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/12/自由時報-暴動小喵出獄-批普廷耍花招/","date":"2013-12-24T01:47:41Z","modified":"2013-12-24T01:47:41Z","title":"自由時報 | 暴動小喵出獄 批普廷耍花招","content":"<p><div><span>暴動小喵出獄 批普廷耍花招</span></p>\n<p><span></p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://redirect.viglink.com/?key=11fe087258b6fc0532a5ccfc924805c0&#038;u=http%3A%2F%2Fiservice.libertytimes.com.tw%2FIService3%2Fnewspic.php%3Fpic%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.libertytimes.com.tw%2F2013%2Fnew%2Fdec%2F24%2Fimages%2FbigPic%2F97.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.libertytimes.com.tw/2013/new/dec/24/images/97.jpg\" border=\"0\"></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>艾廖希娜（法新社 ）</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p><span>俄羅斯女子龐克樂團「暴動小喵」（Pussy Riot）上週獲得特赦後，成員托洛科尼可娃（Nadezhda Tolokonnikova）和艾廖希娜（Maria Alyokhina ）二十三日先後獲釋出獄。兩人係因在莫斯科最大教堂聖壇表演「龐克祈禱」遭判刑兩年，服刑一年十個月後重獲自由，成為當局壓制民間異議人士的象徵。托洛科尼可娃抨擊俄國監獄體制，指控俄國是按照罪犯流放地而建立，她今後將集中心力關切罪犯人權。艾廖希娜也抨擊這次特赦是總統普廷為了索契冬季奧運而使出的公關花招，「如果我可以選擇拒絕，我會這麼做。」</span></p>\n<p></span></div>\n<p><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\"></p>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheet/embeddedform?hl=zh-CN&#038;formkey=dGRpN3FrVThuMFFsZHBZcmNGLW94dEE6MQ\" width=\"510\" height=\"326\" frameborder=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\">Loading&#8230;</iframe></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":1000,"categories":[18270,18269,18424],"tags":[11945]}